snippet.title: Seek and Dread Online
snippet.description:
www.seekanddread.de

This is a video of me playing Seek and Dread Online. Seek and Dread is an Online shoot 'em up game, similar to that of Counter Strike. It is made with a program used Multimedia Fusion 2. To find out more about Multimedia Fusion 2  , then pelase visit, the creators website, www.clickteam.com

To download Seek and Dread Online, goto  www.seekanddread.de - the game is very fun and also includes an excellent map editor, if you wish to make your own maps, so you can host them and other can download them.

The music is from the game, I converted the mods to wavs using winamp and then converted them from wav files to mp3 using Switch.

To edit the video I used Sony Vegas.
